official_title: A bill to impose quantitative limitations on the importation of shrimp into the United States during calendar years 1975 and 1976, and to impose a duty on imported shrimp.

summary.text: Imposes quantitative limitations under the Tariff Schedules of the United States on the importation of shrimp into the United States during calendar years 1975 and 1976. Imposes an import duty on imported shrimp.

titles.title: A bill to impose quantitative limitations on the importation of shrimp into the United States during calendar years 1975 and 1976, and to impose a duty on imported shrimp.
